title: symtab: not defined (and others)
body:
What steps will reproduce the problem?

jasmuth@dice:~/gospace$ cat test.go
package main

func main() {
     println("Hello!")
}
jasmuth@dice:~/gospace$ 6g test.go 
jasmuth@dice:~/gospace$ ls
test.6  test.go
jasmuth@dice:~/gospace$ 6l test.6
MHeapMap_Preallocate: symtab: not defined
MHeapMap_Preallocate: esymtab: not defined
MHeapMap_Preallocate: pclntab: not defined
MHeapMap_Preallocate: epclntab: not defined

What is the expected output?

Hello!

Which compiler are you using (5g, 6g, 8g, gccgo)?

6g

Which operating system are you using?

Ubuntu

Which revision are you using?  (hg identify)

jasmuth@dice:~/userland/go$ hg identify
6f22a696557f+ tip
